00087 DataSetHeader *CHPMultiDataData::GetDataSetHeader(MultiDataType dataType)
00088 {
00089     int n = genericData.Header().GetDataGroup(0).GetDataSetCnt();
00090     for (int i=0; i<n; i++)
00091     {
00092         DataSetHeader &h = genericData.Header().GetDataGroup(0).GetDataSet(i);
00093         if (h.GetName() == MultiDataDataSetNames[(int)dataType])
00094             return &h;
00095     }
00096     return NULL;

00257 void CHPMultiDataData::GetExtraMetricEntries(DataSetInfo *ds, int rowIndex, int colIndex, std::vector<affymetrix_calvin_parameter::ParameterNameValueType> &metrics)
00258 {
00259         int32_t ncols = (int32_t) ds->metricColumns.size();
00260         metrics.resize(ncols);
00261         for (int32_t icol=0; icol<ncols; icol++)

00263                 metrics[icol].SetName(ds->metricColumns[icol].GetName());
00264                 switch (ds->metricColumns[icol].GetColumnType())
00265                 {
00266                         case ByteColType:
00267                                 {
00268                                         int8_t val;
00269                                         ds->entries->GetData(rowIndex, colIndex++, val);
00270                                         metrics[icol].SetValueInt8(val);
00271                                 }
00272                                 break;
00273 
00274                         case UByteColType:
00275                                 {
00276                                         u_int8_t val;
00277                                         ds->entries->GetData(rowIndex, colIndex++, val);
00278                                         metrics[icol].SetValueUInt8(val);
00279                                 }
00280                                 break;
00281 
00282                         case ShortColType:
00283                                 {
00284                                         int16_t val;
00285                                         ds->entries->GetData(rowIndex, colIndex++, val);
00286                                         metrics[icol].SetValueInt16(val);
00287                                 }
00288                                 break;
00289 
00290                         case UShortColType:
00291                                 {
00292                                         u_int16_t val;
00293                                         ds->entries->GetData(rowIndex, colIndex++, val);
00294                                         metrics[icol].SetValueUInt16(val);
00295                                 }
00296                                 break;
00297 
00298                         case IntColType:
00299                                 {
00300                                         int32_t val;
00301                                         ds->entries->GetData(rowIndex, colIndex++, val);
00302                                         metrics[icol].SetValueInt32(val);
00303                                 }
00304                                 break;
00305 
00306                         case UIntColType:
00307                                 {
00308                                         u_int32_t val;
00309                                         ds->entries->GetData(rowIndex, colIndex++, val);
00310                                         metrics[icol].SetValueUInt32(val);
00311                                 }
00312                                 break;
00313 
00314                         case FloatColType:
00315                                 {
00316                                         float val;
00317                                         ds->entries->GetData(rowIndex, colIndex++, val);
00318                                         metrics[icol].SetValueFloat(val);
00319                                 }
00320                                 break;
00321 
00322                         case ASCIICharColType:
00323                                 {
00324                                         string val;

00377 void CHPMultiDataData::AddColumns(DataSetInfo &info, DataSetHeader& hdr)
00378 {
00379     switch (info.dataType)
00380     {
00381     case ExpressionMultiDataType:
00382         hdr.AddAsciiColumn(PROBE_SET_NAME, info.maxProbeSetName);
00383         hdr.AddFloatColumn(EXPRESSION_QUANTIFICATION_NAME);
00384         break;
00385         
00386     case GenotypeMultiDataType:
00387         hdr.AddAsciiColumn(PROBE_SET_NAME, info.maxProbeSetName);
00388         hdr.AddUByteColumn(GENOTYPE_CALL_NAME);
00389         hdr.AddFloatColumn(GENOTYPE_CONFIDENCE_NAME);
00390         break;
00391 
00392     case CopyNumberMultiDataType:
00393         hdr.AddAsciiColumn(PROBE_SET_NAME, info.maxProbeSetName);
00394         hdr.AddUByteColumn(COPY_NUMBER_CHR_NAME);
00395         hdr.AddUIntColumn(COPY_NUMBER_POSITION_NAME);
00396         break;
00397 
00398     case CytoMultiDataType:
00399         hdr.AddAsciiColumn(CYTO_REGION_NAME, info.maxProbeSetName);
00400         hdr.AddUByteColumn(CYTO_CHR_NAME);
00401         hdr.AddUIntColumn(CYTO_START_POSITION_NAME);
00402         hdr.AddUIntColumn(CYTO_STOP_POSITION_NAME);
00403         hdr.AddUByteColumn(CYTO_CALL_NAME);
00404         hdr.AddFloatColumn(CYTO_CONFIDENCE_NAME);
00405         break;
00406 
00407     default:
00408         break;
00409     }
00410 
00411     for (vector<ColumnInfo>::iterator it=info.metricColumns.begin(); it!=info.metricColumns.end(); ++it)
00412         {
00413                 hdr.AddColumn(*it);
00414         }
00415 }

00417 DataSetInfo *CHPMultiDataData::OpenMultiDataDataSet(MultiDataType dataType)
00418 {
00419     map<MultiDataType, DataSetInfo>::iterator pos = dataSetInfo.find(dataType);
00420         if (pos != dataSetInfo.end())
00421                 return &dataSetInfo[dataType];
00422 
00423     DataSetInfo info;
00424     info.entries = genericData.DataSet(MULTI_DATA_NAME, MultiDataDataSetNames[dataType]);
00425         if (info.entries)
00426         {
00427                 info.entries->Open();
00428                 int32_t ncols = info.entries->Header().GetColumnCnt();
00429                 info.metricColumns.clear();
00430         int startCol = 0;
00431         if (dataType == ExpressionMultiDataType)
00432             startCol = 2;
00433         else if (dataType == GenotypeMultiDataType)
00434             startCol = 3;
00435         else if (dataType == CopyNumberMultiDataType)
00436             startCol = 3;
00437         else if (dataType == CytoMultiDataType)
00438             startCol = 6;
00439 
00440                 for (int32_t icol=startCol; icol<ncols; icol++)
00441                 {
00442             info.metricColumns.push_back(info.entries->Header().GetColumnInfo(icol));
00443                 }
00444         dataSetInfo[dataType] = info;
00445         return &dataSetInfo[dataType];
00446         }
00447     return NULL;
00448 }

00480 ParameterNameValueTypeList CHPMultiDataData::GetAlgParams()
00481 {
00482         ParameterNameValueTypeList nvt;
00483         ParameterNameValueTypeIt begin, end;
00484         ParameterNameValueType param;
00485 
00486         genericData.Header().GetGenericDataHdr()->GetNameValIterators(begin, end);
00487         while(begin != end)
00488         {
00489                 std::wstring key = begin->GetName();
00490                 if(key.compare(0, ALGORITHM_PARAM_NAME_PREFIX_S.size(),ALGORITHM_PARAM_NAME_PREFIX_S) == 0)
00491                 {
00492                         param = *begin;
00493                         key.erase(0, ALGORITHM_PARAM_NAME_PREFIX_S.size());
00494                         param.SetName(key);
00495                         nvt.push_back(param);
00496                 }
00497                 begin++;
00498         }
00499         return nvt;
00500 }
